35,美国,对华援助协会,China Aid Association,对华援助协会是一个国际非营利基督教人权组织，致力于在中国促进宗教自由和法治。,对华援助协会成立于2002年，20年来一直致力于揭露人权侵犯行为，通过倡导中国的宗教自由和法治来促进真理、正义和自由。协会的历史包括为非法监禁的受害者提供法律援助、发布中国家庭教会受迫害的年度报告、协助中国家庭教会和人权律师、组织宗教自由论坛、揭露新疆少数民族的大规模监禁等。2022年，协会庆祝了成立20周年。,对华援助协会由创始人Bob Fu领导，他是一位在中国出生并成长的人权活动家。协会设有顾问委员会，由高影响力的个人组成，为宗教自由倡议提供智慧和有效性。此外，协会还有合作伙伴网络，包括倡导宗教自由、人权和法治的组织。协会的日常运作由一支热情的团队负责。,"[""https://chinaaid.org/news/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/maizhong-reformed-church-in-anhui-fuyang-was-raided-again-on-sunday-many-individuals-were-taken-away-by-the-police-and-their-whereabouts-are-unknown/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/pingyang-detention-center-is-accused-of-abuse-of-power-a-meeting-between-the-lawyers-and-pastor-huang-yizi-is-obstructed/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/analysis-of-the-case-of-the-maizhong-reformed-church-in-fuyang-anhui-escalating-religious-persecution-and-legal-challenges/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/early-rain-covenant-church-member-chen-jiaozhi-was-barred-from-leaving-the-country-reportedly-due-to-her-clothing-bearing-the-church-logo/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/the-tenth-anniversary-of-the-709-case-raises-awareness-about-xie-yangs-1000-days-of-arbitrary-detention-and-un-concerns/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/wenzhou-pastor-huang-yizi-is-criminally-detained-again-christians-regard-it-as-religious-persecution/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/chen-xianyan-and-three-other-christians-face-over-three-years-in-prison-for-organizing-or-using-a-cult-organization-in-nanning/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/members-of-linfen-house-churches-sentenced-heavily-again-china-aid-association-urges-trump-administration-to-speak-out/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/we-were-not-defrauded-members-of-the-xian-church-of-abundance-jointly-issued-a-statement-to-refute-the-fraud-accusation/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/zhejiang-pastor-huang-yizi-detained-again-by-authorities-on-suspicion-of-illegal-business-operations/"", ""https://chinaaid.org/news/university-of-notre-dame-law-schools-relig