47,美国,阿特拉斯网络,Atlas Network,ATLAS网络是在911袭击后通过警察局长特遣队的倡议下成立[1][2]，该组织最初是为促进各欧盟成员国特种警察单位之间的信息交流和训练活动而非正式建立，后来由理事会在 2008年的一项决议正式成立，该决定还扩大了ATLAS的功能，包括应请求向另一个成员国提供援助[3]。ATLAS内部使用的“特别干预单位”和“危急情况”两个术语被定义为：“特别干预单位”是指任何一个具备应对危急情况能力的成员国执法单位。“危急情况”是指任何成员国当局有合理理由相信存在对该成员国的人员、财产、基础设施或机构构成严重直接人身威胁的刑事犯罪，特别是在打击恐怖主义的情况下的任何情况。ATLAS意识到某些成员国可能不具备有效处理所有危急情况的手段、资源或专业知识，特别是大型危急情况，并让各成员国请求另一个成员国给予援助提供了框架。,,,"[""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/hope-iran-and-the-power-of-civil-society-with-mohamad-machine-chian"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/how-quiet-leadership-transformed"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/europe-liberty-forum-2025-brings-freedom-champions-to-brussels"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/bitcoin-freedom-global-disruption"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/nataliya-melnyk-2025-europe-smart-bets-pitch-competition"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/georgias-future-academy-wins-ela-2025"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/enhancing-student-talent-recruitment"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/hope-after-tyranny"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/announce-young-journalism-prize-2025"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/from-the-farm-to-freedom"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/beyond-aid"", ""https://www.atlasnetwork.org/articles/what-freedom-really-looks-like""]",2025-07-04 18:14:29,[]
