[ ![a photo of the Eisenhower Executive Office Building](https://www.defense.gov/portals/1/Interactive/2023/11-historyofdod/1800s-images/10-1889.jpeg) ](https://www.defense.gov/Portals/1/Interactive/2023/11-historyofdod/1800s-images/10-1889.jpeg)
