The [United States goes to war with Spain](https://www.defense.gov/Multimedia/Experience/The-History-of-the-Department-of-Defense/) in support of Cuban independence and in response to the sinking of the battleship USS Maine in Havana Harbor.
[ ![A map of the Spanish-American War](https://www.defense.gov/portals/1/Interactive/2023/11-historyofdod/1800s-images/11-feb1899.jpeg) ](https://www.defense.gov/Portals/1/Interactive/2023/11-historyofdod/1800s-images/11-feb1899.jpeg)
