## We are the Nation’s first line of defense. We accomplish what others cannot accomplish and go where others cannot go.
![](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20height='504'%20width='504'%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20version='1.1'%3E%3C/svg%3E)
